    text = _OKAI_EDGE_BASE_BUILD_SETTINGS_TEXT()
    return text + "\n\nPositive Edge Learning:\nON. It learns profitable CE/PE time buckets and gives score/fake-risk support to proven A-grade setups.\n\nPeak Trail Fix:\nON. Trailing SL now updates the option premium peak and uses max(cost+charges+5%, 1R trail, peak minus 5%). Paper SL fills are recorded at the stop price instead of the next lower observed LTP."


